                            <comment id="13197155" author="tomwhite" created="Tue, 31 Jan 2012 19:41:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I wonder if &lt;tt&gt;touch TouchedFileInsideGrunt_61 | ls&lt;/tt&gt; is causing a race, we should probably change it to &lt;tt&gt;touch TouchedFileInsideGrunt_61 &amp;amp;&amp;amp; ls&lt;/tt&gt; for safety&apos;s sake anyway.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2206&quot; title=&quot;Make Pig unit test work on Mac&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2206&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2206&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was reporting this test as failing too. I don&apos;t think it&apos;s Mac specific as I have seen this failure on Linux too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
